# Localization And Spellcheck

- RULE: Keep doctrine, rules, configs, and contributor docs in English.
- RULE: Allow Spanish only in explicit user-facing artifacts covered by ADR.
- RULE: Keep localization resources in embedded JSON with English fallback.
- RULE: User-facing desktop language selection is limited to English and Spanish.
- RULE: Maintain manual cspell dictionaries instead of broad language-pack exceptions.
